   <section id="Section545195">
      <title>
          
         <indexterm significance="normal">
            <primary>sales</primary>
            <secondary>taxable summarized</secondary>
         </indexterm>Summarized Taxable Sales</title>
      <para id="Para639975">The Summarized Taxable Sales display enables you to
    determine the amount of sales Tax you have billed over a given period of
    time. To view a summary of taxable sales, select the "Summarized Taxable
    Sales" option from the "Displays" menu. The following screen will
    appear:</para>
      <para id="Para533568">
         <screenshot>
            <mediaobject>
               <imageobject>
                  <imagedata fileref="images/SO_Disp_sumTaxSales.png" id="Graphic533566"/>
               </imageobject>
               <caption id="Caption533569">Summarized Taxable Sales</caption>
            </mediaobject>
         </screenshot>
      </para>
      <para id="Para533570">When displaying summarized taxable sales, you are
    presented with the following options:</para>
      <variablelist>
         <varlistentry>
            <term id="Para533594">All Tax Codes</term>
            <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1992eb8">
               <para>Select to display summarized taxable Sales for all Tax
          Codes.</para>
            </listitem>
         </varlistentry>
         <varlistentry>
            <term id="Para533595">Selected</term>
            <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1992f00">
               <para>Specify Tax Code whose summarized taxable Sales you want to
          display.</para>
            </listitem>
         </varlistentry>
         <varlistentry>
            <term id="Para533600">Start Ship Date</term>
            <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1992f48">
               <para>Taxable sales transactions occurring on or after this date
          will display.</para>
            </listitem>
         </varlistentry>
         <varlistentry>
            <term id="Para533605">End Ship Date</term>
            <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1992f90">
               <para>Taxable sales transactions occurring on or before this date
          will display.</para>
            </listitem>
         </varlistentry>
         <varlistentry>
            <term id="Para533607">Summarized Sales</term>
            <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1992fd8">
               <para>Display lists summarized sales using the specified
          parameters.</para>
            </listitem>
         </varlistentry>
      </variablelist>
      <para id="Para533609">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>
      <variablelist>
         <varlistentry>
            <term id="Para533610">CLOSE</term>
            <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1993044">
               <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
          desktop.</para>
            </listitem>
         </varlistentry>
         <varlistentry>
            <term id="Para653808">PRINT</term>
            <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x199308c">
               <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
            </listitem>
         </varlistentry>
      </variablelist>
   </section>